---
---
<section id="services" style="background-color: var(--color-secondary); padding: var(--space-xl) 0; border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);">
  <div class="section-pad" style="padding-top: 0; padding-bottom: 0;">
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);">
      <h2 style="font-size: var(--text-4xl);">Core <span class="text-accent">Capabilities</span></h2>
      <p style="margin: 0 auto;">We don't build generic software. We engineer specific, high-ROI agent frameworks designed specifically to solve complex enterprise dragging points.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-3">
      
      <div class="card">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17.5 19V9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2h-7a2 2 0 0 0-2 2v10"></path><path d="M4 19h16"></path><path d="M9 19v-4h3v4"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Cloud-Based AI Systems</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 0;">
          Custom software architectures that utilize AI to automate heavy backend tasks. Proven track record of implementing AI-assisted systems for agency clients that directly generate multi-million dollar contract savings.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="22 12 18 12 15 21 9 3 6 12 2 12"></polyline></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Automated Outreach</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 0;">
          Stop relying on manual SDRs to hit pipeline goals. We construct end-to-end automated engagement platforms featuring AI-driven personalization, reliably delivering 300%+ net pipeline growth.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="card">
        <div style="margin-bottom: 1rem;">
          <svg width="32" height="32" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="var(--color-accent)" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"></circle><path d="M19.4 15a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33 1.82l.06.06a2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83 2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0l-.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82-.33 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1 1.51V21a2 2 0 0 1-2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 9 19.4a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.82.33l-.06.06a2 2 0 0 1-2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83l.06-.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 .33-1.82 1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51-1H3a2 2 0 0 1-2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2-2h.09A1.65 1.65 0 0 0 4.6 9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33-1.82l-.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 0-2.83 2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0l.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82.33H9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1-1.51V3a2 2 0 0 1 2-2 2 2 0 0 1 2 2v.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1 1.51 1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.82-.33l.06-.06a2 2 0 0 1 2.83 0 2 2 0 0 1 0 2.83l-.06.06a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-.33 1.82V9a1.65 1.65 0 0 0 1.51 1H21a2 2 0 0 1 2 2 2 2 0 0 1-2 2h-.09a1.65 1.65 0 0 0-1.51 1z"></path></svg>
        </div>
        <h3>Agent-Based Workflows</h3>
        <p style="font-size: var(--text-base); margin-bottom: 0;">
          Multi-agent orchestration to compile, synthesize, and create executive-ready deliverables with strictly zero administrative oversight. Independent, parallelized, and perfectly accurate.
        </p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</section>
